      "height": 140,
      "text": "FastAPI (Python 3.11)\n\napi_routes.py  → JSON API\nroutes.py      → SSR HTML\npipeline.py    → 4-Stage Engine\nbackground.py  → Async Runner\ncache.py       → Prompt Cache\nscorer.py      → 2-dim Score",
